1269
01:16:14,200 --> 01:16:16,240
The council members
will have to be quick.

1270
01:16:16,370 --> 01:16:18,040
To heck with them!

1271
01:16:18,370 --> 01:16:20,540
Even if they declare
Shahrukh to be a Hindu

1272
01:16:20,660 --> 01:16:23,330
Sheikh would still not care.

1273
01:16:24,040 --> 01:16:26,800
Who better than
Sheikh to spot a messiah?

1274
01:16:27,960 --> 01:16:29,670
The Quran originated from there.

1275
01:16:31,300 --> 01:16:32,300
Am I right, priest?

1276
01:16:33,090 --> 01:16:34,090
Let's go home.
- Yes.

1277
01:16:34,220 --> 01:16:36,300
Come on. Come on.
- Let's go.

1278
01:17:06,670 --> 01:17:08,290
Hello, ma'am.

1279
01:17:09,550 --> 01:17:11,460
Sir..
I am also there.

1280
01:17:12,670 --> 01:17:14,430
Hello, priest.
- Hello.

1281
01:17:16,260 --> 01:17:17,970
Are you going somewhere, ma'am?

1282
01:17:18,180 --> 01:17:20,060
Yes, child.
I am going to my mother's place.

1283
01:17:20,270 --> 01:17:21,810
It's better than
going to prison.

1284
01:17:23,730 --> 01:17:25,940
Prison?
What are you saying, ma'am?

1285
01:17:26,810 --> 01:17:28,940
I have brought sweets
for all of you.

1286
01:17:31,820 --> 01:17:35,530
I have got a job in
a big salon in Mumbai.

1287
01:17:36,610 --> 01:17:38,450
That's great news, child!

1288
01:17:38,830 --> 01:17:41,200
Child, take me along with you.
- Yes. Everyone can go.

1289
01:17:41,330 --> 01:17:44,830
I am here to get
beaten by the police.

1290
01:17:45,250 --> 01:17:46,290
Police?

1291
01:17:48,290 --> 01:17:49,340
What's the matter?

1292
01:17:52,090 --> 01:17:53,090
Sir, what is the matter?

1293
01:17:56,510 --> 01:17:57,640
Mr. Sheikh is coming.

1294
01:17:57,800 --> 01:18:00,430
Now what to do?
We can't stay here.

1295
01:18:02,470 --> 01:18:04,810
But why to leave the village?

1296
01:18:05,730 --> 01:18:08,360
What if he finds out
Shahrukh' s truth?

1297
01:18:08,520 --> 01:18:10,320
Shahrukh' s truth?

1298
01:18:10,440 --> 01:18:12,690
That his father Kalia
is a non-Muslim.

1299
01:18:13,320 --> 01:18:16,070
Now they are saying, he is
the incarnation of Lord Shiva.

1300
01:18:16,360 --> 01:18:17,740
Trident. God forbid.

1301
01:18:18,370 --> 01:18:21,530
Who knows what decision
the council will take, and when?

1302
01:18:22,740 --> 01:18:24,200
Priest, that's a good thing.

1303
01:18:24,540 --> 01:18:25,960
What's the worse
that will happen?

1304
01:18:26,210 --> 01:18:28,170
Mr. Sheikh won't take
Shahrukh with him.

1305
01:18:28,920 --> 01:18:30,880
The matter will end.
It's good.

1306
01:18:31,170 --> 01:18:32,750
Yes. And then we
will go to prison.

1307
01:18:33,210 --> 01:18:34,260
Why prison?

1308
01:18:34,590 --> 01:18:37,970
Sir, the claim not being
proven is not an offense.

1309
01:18:38,130 --> 01:18:40,470
But not returning 50,000
is a crime, isn't it?

1310
01:18:41,600 --> 01:18:43,260
You took money?

1311
01:18:44,140 --> 01:18:47,350
We asked for an advance.
And he immediately agreed.

1312
01:18:47,810 --> 01:18:49,230
Ask them where the money went.

1313
01:18:50,520 --> 01:18:52,400
Ma'am, where is the money?

1314
01:18:52,770 --> 01:18:54,780
Only Rs. 5,000 is left.
- What?

1315
01:18:55,150 --> 01:18:58,660
Forget that.
No one cared for me here.

1316
01:18:58,780 --> 01:19:00,700
You hardly will, when
I go to my mother's place.

1317
01:19:00,820 --> 01:19:03,580
But where did such
a hefty sum go?

1318
01:19:03,700 --> 01:19:06,830
The party workers took
away half as donation.

1319
01:19:08,040 --> 01:19:10,330
Okay. I am going.
I won't stay here.

1320
01:19:10,460 --> 01:19:13,090
Come on. Pick up the bags.
Pack your bags.

1321
01:19:13,800 --> 01:19:15,130
Yes. Go to the city.

1322
01:19:22,050 --> 01:19:25,390
Fine. If this is the matter

1323
01:19:28,270 --> 01:19:29,560
let's leave together.

1324
01:19:29,690 --> 01:19:30,650
What?
- What?

1325
01:19:31,060 --> 01:19:33,520
Yes. Come on.

1326
01:19:43,490 --> 01:19:46,490
Why is it taking so long?
Where are they?

1327
01:19:47,080 --> 01:19:48,580
Did that boy run away again?

1328
01:19:49,500 --> 01:19:51,420
Where will he go?
As it is, Shahrukh is not..

1329
01:19:51,540 --> 01:19:53,080
Don't take that wretch's name.

1330
01:19:53,250 --> 01:19:55,300
We are in trouble
because of him.

1331
01:19:57,010 --> 01:19:59,470
I am sure something is wrong.
- Yes.

1332
01:19:59,590 --> 01:20:01,300
Why are you worried?
He will come.

1333
01:20:01,430 --> 01:20:03,930
What do you mean?
We need to get away.

1334
01:20:04,050 --> 01:20:05,850
You don't understand. - We will
leave. Everything will be fine.

1335
01:20:05,970 --> 01:20:07,680
With God's grace everything
will be fine. Don't worry.

1336
01:20:07,810 --> 01:20:10,890
Look, a vehicle is coming.
- They are there.

1337
01:20:11,140 --> 01:20:13,230
Stop. Pull over.
- Look. Get up.

1338
01:20:13,400 --> 01:20:14,440
See whose vehicle it is?

1339
01:20:15,070 --> 01:20:18,110
It's ours!
Come on. Let's go.

1340
01:20:18,440 --> 01:20:19,690
Pick up the bags.

1341
01:20:22,820 --> 01:20:23,820
Pick it up.
- Has everyone come?

1342
01:20:24,120 --> 01:20:25,240
Come on.
- Let's go.

1343
01:20:25,780 --> 01:20:28,830
The luggage.. Ma'am,
all of you get into the vehicle.

1344
01:20:29,370 --> 01:20:30,410
I will load the bags.

1345
01:20:30,540 --> 01:20:31,500
Okay.
- All of you sit comfortably.

1346
01:20:31,620 --> 01:20:34,790
Okay.
- Sit. Sit. Come on. Let's go.

1347
01:20:34,920 --> 01:20:37,880
Wait. - Why are you sitting
in the front? Let him sit.

1348
01:20:38,000 --> 01:20:39,260
Priest.
- Come on.

1349
01:20:39,380 --> 01:20:41,010
You sit.
Ma'am, I am there.

1350
01:20:41,130 --> 01:20:43,340
Let him sit. We youngsters
will sit in the rear.

1351
01:20:43,470 --> 01:20:46,140
He will manage. Let's go.
- Hurry up. Come on.

1352
01:20:46,260 --> 01:20:47,310
Get in. Get in.
- Sit comfortably.

1353
01:20:47,430 --> 01:20:50,140
Sit. Come on.

1354
01:20:54,190 --> 01:20:55,230
Come. Come, lad. Very good.

1355
01:20:55,400 --> 01:20:58,020
May God bless you
with prosperity, lad.

1356
01:20:58,320 --> 01:21:00,570
Not prosperity.
Just a beautiful girl. Yes.

1357
01:21:00,820 --> 01:21:03,450
Get that bag too.

1358
01:21:05,700 --> 01:21:06,740
Okay. Come on.

1359
01:21:08,450 --> 01:21:09,580
Come on. Let's go.

1360
01:21:32,060 --> 01:21:33,690
Murli, what happened?

1361
01:21:33,810 --> 01:21:36,060
I don't know. The vehicle is not
starting. I need the tool box.

1362
01:21:36,440 --> 01:21:38,820
Is that so? I will give you.
I know where the tool box is.

1363
01:21:38,940 --> 01:21:39,940
Wait.

1364
01:21:41,480 --> 01:21:42,440
Take this.

1365
01:21:45,320 --> 01:21:47,030
The goat has also come along?

1366
01:21:47,160 --> 01:21:49,450
What happened?
- What's going on?

1367
01:21:49,580 --> 01:21:51,290
Repair the vehicle. Repair
the vehicle. Repair the vehicle.

1368
01:21:51,410 --> 01:21:53,910
Why did you bring him?
Why did you bring him?

1369
01:21:54,040 --> 01:21:55,210
Say something.

1370
01:21:57,540 --> 01:21:58,840
What have you done?

1371
01:21:59,090 --> 01:22:00,130
Oh, God!

1372
01:22:01,380 --> 01:22:04,380
Zulfi, are you crazy?
- Don't scold Zulfi.

1373
01:22:06,680 --> 01:22:08,970
You have put us
in serious trouble.

1374
01:22:10,140 --> 01:22:12,390
People think he is God.

1375
01:22:12,600 --> 01:22:14,890
We had to flee at night
because of this wretch.

1376
01:22:15,020 --> 01:22:17,020
Don't scold Shahrukh.
- Beware!

1377
01:22:17,190 --> 01:22:20,320
If he had not been there,
we wouldn't have been slandered.

1378
01:22:20,440 --> 01:22:22,730
He didn't do anything.
We did it.

1379
01:22:22,860 --> 01:22:24,820
What?
- What did you do?

1380
01:22:25,740 --> 01:22:26,820
Zulfi is right.

1381
01:22:28,700 --> 01:22:30,830
We made this symbol on Shahrukh.

1382
01:22:35,620 --> 01:22:37,330
I made it.
- What?

1383
01:22:40,040 --> 01:22:41,340
You made this symbol?

1384
01:22:42,500 --> 01:22:45,670
Yes. I wrote 'Lord' on him.

1385
01:22:45,880 --> 01:22:46,970
Oh God!

1386
01:22:48,760 --> 01:22:49,720
What else could I do?

1387
01:22:50,850 --> 01:22:52,260
You wanted to sell Shahrukh.

1388
01:22:52,680 --> 01:22:54,310
Zulfi didn't want him
to go anywhere.

1389
01:22:54,680 --> 01:22:59,190
Zulfi wanted Shahrukh.
All of you wanted money.

1390
01:22:59,770 --> 01:23:02,570
Why didn't both of you tell us
for so many days?

1391
01:23:03,070 --> 01:23:04,360
What will happen now?

1392
01:23:04,780 --> 01:23:08,070
Nothing will happen.
Everyone knows the truth.

1393
01:23:08,780 --> 01:23:09,950
Let's return to the village.

1394
01:23:10,120 --> 01:23:14,450
Shut up!
- What? You are a fool!

1395
01:23:17,160 --> 01:23:19,120
What do we do now?
- What else?

1396
01:23:19,250 --> 01:23:21,080
We will do what we were doing.
Let's flee.

1397
01:23:21,630 --> 01:23:23,840
Murli, did you fix the vehicle?
Yes, sir. The vehicle has been fixed.

1398
01:23:23,960 --> 01:23:25,630
Come on. Sit in the vehicle.
Let's go. Hurry up.

1399
01:23:26,210 --> 01:23:27,260
Zulfi, come on.

1400
01:23:27,550 --> 01:23:28,880
Come on. Sit in the vehicle.

1401
01:23:29,130 --> 01:23:30,180
Ma'am.
- Come on. - Sir.

1402
01:23:30,840 --> 01:23:33,560
Get him in.
- Yes, priest. You sit as well.

1403
01:23:40,810 --> 01:23:42,400
Let's go.
- Hurry up.

1404
01:23:42,520 --> 01:23:43,570
Murli.

1405
01:23:43,770 --> 01:23:46,940
"O' Prince.. You'll not be spared."

1406
01:23:47,070 --> 01:23:50,240
"O' Prince.. You'll not be spared."

1407
01:23:50,360 --> 01:23:53,530
"Forget the wedding or love.
It's all in ruins now."

1408
01:23:53,950 --> 01:23:59,830
"You lost your way.
Love has made you blind."

1409
01:23:59,960 --> 01:24:05,130
"You lost your way.
Love has made you blind."

1410
01:24:16,850 --> 01:24:20,060
"Look, who has come."

1411
01:24:20,940 --> 01:24:24,060
"He has captured the world."

1412
01:24:24,940 --> 01:24:28,110
"Everyone's eyes are on him."

1413
01:24:28,900 --> 01:24:32,160
"Arms have opened for him."

1414
01:24:40,620 --> 01:24:45,460
"Recognize me. I am Don."

1415
01:24:45,710 --> 01:24:46,750
Sir.

1416
01:24:48,210 --> 01:24:49,210
Let us pass, sir.

1417
01:24:49,340 --> 01:24:50,550
What?
- Let us pass.

1418
01:24:52,340 --> 01:24:54,140
Show the papers.
- They are in the car.

1419
01:24:56,050 --> 01:24:57,010
So bring them.

1420
01:25:00,430 --> 01:25:02,980
What do you think?
Can we extract something?

1421
01:25:04,230 --> 01:25:05,400
We will.

1422
01:25:07,900 --> 01:25:10,690
Looks like the police
have found out everything.

1423
01:25:10,820 --> 01:25:13,150
What nonsense! Keep quiet.

1424
01:25:13,320 --> 01:25:15,120
You don't have any brains.
You just keep talking nonsense.

1425
01:25:15,240 --> 01:25:17,450
Keep quiet. They are coming.
- Keep quiet.

1426
01:25:23,960 --> 01:25:25,920
From where?
- Who?

1427
01:25:27,460 --> 01:25:29,750
From which village
is your father from?

1428
01:25:29,960 --> 01:25:31,170
Mangori.

1429
01:25:34,680 --> 01:25:35,840
Where are you going?

1430
01:25:36,510 --> 01:25:38,600
We are going to Mumbai, sir.

1431
01:25:40,600 --> 01:25:44,020
Come on. Come out.

1432
01:25:49,400 --> 01:25:51,530
Hello, sir.
Sir, there are women.

1433
01:25:51,740 --> 01:25:55,610
We will check who are behind
the veil. Men or women.

1434
01:25:55,740 --> 01:25:58,200
Hurry up.
- Sir, I am from Mumbai.

1435
01:25:59,080 --> 01:26:01,450
I work in Mumbai. Hair stylist.

1436
01:26:01,620 --> 01:26:03,120
They are my relatives.

1437
01:26:03,710 --> 01:26:04,660
They are coming
to Mumbai with me.

1438
01:26:04,790 --> 01:26:06,460
I see. So you are the leader.

1439
01:26:06,920 --> 01:26:08,710
Where do you work in Mumbai?

1440
01:26:08,840 --> 01:26:10,710
You make bombs?
- Barber.

1441
01:26:10,840 --> 01:26:13,630
You make bombs,
acid and its likes in Mumbai.

1442
01:26:14,050 --> 01:26:16,090
What is in the vehicle?
- Nothing, sir. Household stuff.

1443
01:26:16,220 --> 01:26:17,220
Move. Show us. Show us. Show us.

1444
01:26:17,390 --> 01:26:18,800
RDX?
- No, sir.

1445
01:26:18,970 --> 01:26:20,970
Provisions. Clothes.
Nothing else.

1446
01:26:23,480 --> 01:26:25,140
What if there is
really a bomb inside?

1447
01:26:26,690 --> 01:26:27,690
What if it explodes?

1448
01:26:28,020 --> 01:26:29,270
What are you saying, sir?

1449
01:26:29,520 --> 01:26:30,570
Is that possible?

1450
01:26:31,150 --> 01:26:32,230
Anything can happen.

1451
01:26:33,490 --> 01:26:34,490
Didn't you see the old man?

1452
01:26:35,860 --> 01:26:37,740
He looks like Osama
Bin Laden's brother.

1453
01:26:38,740 --> 01:26:41,490
That Osama?
- Yes. That very Osama.

1454
01:26:42,200 --> 01:26:43,160
What do we do?

1455
01:26:45,250 --> 01:26:46,870
Hero. Come here.

1456
01:26:47,330 --> 01:26:48,460
Open the door.

1457
01:26:48,670 --> 01:26:51,380
Open it.
- Open it. Open it.

1458
01:26:51,800 --> 01:26:53,800
I am opening it, sir.
- Shall I hit you? No.

1459
01:26:54,210 --> 01:26:55,300
Open it.

1460
01:27:01,600 --> 01:27:04,140
Sir, it is a goat.
- What?

1461
01:27:04,430 --> 01:27:05,600
There is a goat and a child.

1462
01:27:08,440 --> 01:27:09,520
Tell me. Tell me.
Who is behind this? No.

1463
01:27:09,650 --> 01:27:13,270
Sir, are they going
to create trouble? No.

1464
01:27:13,400 --> 01:27:15,190
Whatever it is.
We can't take a chance.

1465
01:27:16,190 --> 01:27:18,660
The minister's function
is not far from here.

1466
01:27:19,320 --> 01:27:21,910
The minister is expected
to stay there for two hours.

1467
01:27:22,530 --> 01:27:25,250
Meanwhile, let them remain here.

1468
01:27:25,700 --> 01:27:28,330
They will stay here until
the function is over.

1469
01:27:28,580 --> 01:27:31,670
Arrest everyone
whom you suspect.

1470
01:27:32,380 --> 01:27:35,050
We will verify later who is
innocent and who is guilty.

1471
01:27:35,840 --> 01:27:40,510
Provide them with all the treatment.
- Sir. Sir, he has fever.

1472
01:27:40,930 --> 01:27:43,890
Look, how he is reclining. If
you could give him some drug..

1473
01:27:44,930 --> 01:27:46,310
I mean, medicine.

1474
01:27:46,430 --> 01:27:48,140
That's the medicine we offer.

1475
01:27:48,690 --> 01:27:50,520
Look. Take a good look.

1476
01:27:51,350 --> 01:27:53,230
This man is a smart chap.

1477
01:27:53,730 --> 01:27:54,690
He has gone to sleep.

1478
01:27:55,150 --> 01:27:57,570
Listen, find yourself a corner.

1479
01:27:58,400 --> 01:27:59,530
Come on.

1480
01:28:01,240 --> 01:28:02,280
Something is fishy.

1481
01:28:03,580 --> 01:28:05,490
I have an experience
of 30 years.

1482
01:28:05,950 --> 01:28:08,120
I can sense it.

1483
01:28:08,910 --> 01:28:10,460
No, sir.
- Sir

1484
01:28:11,080 --> 01:28:15,130
we had a doubt when
we opened the door.

1485
01:28:15,340 --> 01:28:18,720
We thought we would
find RDX, bombs.

1486
01:28:19,550 --> 01:28:23,050
Instead, we found a goat.
All are fools.

1487
01:28:23,970 --> 01:28:25,220
If they are fools,
we will let them go

1488
01:28:25,760 --> 01:28:27,310
once the minister leaves.

1489
01:28:27,930 --> 01:28:29,100
We have got orders
from our superiors.

1490
01:28:30,230 --> 01:28:31,690
Can't afford to take risk.

1491
01:28:32,020 --> 01:28:33,310
That's it.

1492
01:28:33,480 --> 01:28:36,360
Sir, we need to frisk the goat.

1493
01:28:37,150 --> 01:28:38,860
Frisk the goat?
- Of course.

1494
01:28:42,490 --> 01:28:44,780
Oh my!
Must weigh 15 kgs.

1495
01:28:45,530 --> 01:28:46,580
What is the market rate?

1496
01:28:47,040 --> 01:28:48,080
I don't know.

1497
01:28:48,410 --> 01:28:50,830
I asked my wife to make
'biryani' once.

1498
01:28:51,540 --> 01:28:53,250
She said, she would
break my bones.

1499
01:28:54,380 --> 01:28:55,880
We can't afford eggs
with our salary.

1500
01:28:56,340 --> 01:28:57,800
Mutton is beyond our reach.

1501
01:28:57,920 --> 01:28:59,380
Here is your chance.

1502
01:29:00,010 --> 01:29:02,800
Biryani. Kebab. Curry.

1503
01:29:03,510 --> 01:29:04,800
First, frisk the goat.

1504
01:29:05,720 --> 01:29:07,930
You don't know,
they fit it anywhere.

1505
01:29:08,060 --> 01:29:09,810
You are right.

1506
01:29:09,930 --> 01:29:12,140
Shinde, shove the stick inside.

1507
01:29:12,270 --> 01:29:13,560
See if it explodes.

1508
01:29:18,190 --> 01:29:19,820
Hold him.
- It is running.

1509
01:29:19,940 --> 01:29:22,070
Yes. - Wait. Come here.
- Stop.

1510
01:29:22,530 --> 01:29:23,950
What is this?

1511
01:29:25,030 --> 01:29:27,370
Oh my! Seems to be
some secret code. - Yes.

1512
01:29:27,530 --> 01:29:29,410
What is going on?
- See this.

1513
01:29:29,540 --> 01:29:30,620
Can you crack this code?

1514
01:29:32,870 --> 01:29:34,330
Code?

1515
01:29:35,040 --> 01:29:36,460
Oh God!

1516
01:29:36,580 --> 01:29:38,420
